{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it-- I think of it, and I think these guards who were ordered to whip, did they really whip me as hard as they did an adult or not?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I wonder about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember that first-- first feel of the whip was so strong that it was like being cut with a knife and my-- my reflex, the natural reflex was-- you know we were supposed to hold on to the table, there were these long tables.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were people being whipped on each side of these long table and to hold onto it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And our-- our clothes were off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, our pants were down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so the first feel of the whip, my hands just flew right back naturally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so the second one I got across my knuckles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after that, it didn't make much difference.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I would give Daniel a pat on the butt, you know, to make him behave or do something that he wasn't-- you know, to stop doing something he was doing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I always felt funny about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my first encounter with our-- our commandant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had encountered him again several times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, after I finished with this construction, the factory, the brush factor, was actually restarted in-- in Plaszow camp and I was able to get a job there, back to where I-- the same job I had when I was in the-- in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until the beginning of 19-- at the end of 1943-- the end of 1943 or maybe the beginning '44.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Schindler had-- was able to establish a sub camp for his workers.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
